a hydrogen bomb.

36
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:39,100
You see, a hydrogen bomb,

37
00:01:39,260 --> 00:01:41,140
also called a thermonuclear bomb,

38
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:43,380
would be a major leap forward for them.

39
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:47,820
They're far more powerful than bombs North
Korea seems to have tested in previous years.

40
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:49,800
But is it true?

41
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:53,860
When US tested a hydrogen bomb in 1971,

42
