it caused a 6.8 earthquake. Last week's North
Korean detonation was only 4.8

43
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:05,639
slightly weaker than the 4.9 earthquake caused
by their 2013 nuclear test,

44
00:02:05,639 --> 00:02:08,170
which was a regular atomic bomb.

45
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:10,229
So what do we actually know?!

46
00:02:10,229 --> 00:02:13,010
"Well, we know it was a nuclear test."

47
00:02:13,010 --> 00:02:15,360
Okay. But what else do we know?

48
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:22,860
"That you may want to derive more information
so that you can improve your analysis of an

49
